latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#AkkadBakkad is not just a show.

It’s Raj beaming with happiness. Albeit in another world.. because his non-stop positive energy made it happen even from there.

It’s Raj’s storytelling (what he loved doing most!). With that infectious smile and that constant spring in his step.. because that’s just him.

It’s Raj’s pride. A story that excited him from the get go and which he executed with his gut. Because he was always a soldier.. a tough and resilient one.

It’s Raj’s excitement. In abundance. Because now it sees the light of day and you all are going to see it. 

He’s left us with this. It’s us too.. because #AkkadBakkad has a piece of our heart in it too. 

Watch #AkkadBakkad on @Primevideoin TODAY, the 3rd of November. 
It’s his love for us. ❤️#RajKaushal #wemissyou #youliveon

latestPosts.caption:
All work and some play to make a perfectly balanced week! 

#allaboutjune #theweekoninstagram #werkandplay #abittaboth

Last night belonged to @ateevanand and @re_ceremonial 
And what a celebration it was!! 
A master class in all things Indian. Indian craft, Indian textile, slow fashion, beautiful people , some stunning jewels, cocktails and a splendid 5 course meal.
There is a reason why I love what I do so much! 
Ateev last night is one for the books!
The pre festive collection is so well detailed, the colours so dreamy, the embroideries so delicate and the textures so luxurious.

All in all Perfection!

Wearing - @re_ceremonial 
HMU - my loveliest @khush.mua 

#receremonial #fashionnightout #collectionlaunch #indiancraft #indiantextile #slowfashion #prefestivecollection

latestPosts.caption:
I always begin the first day of the week with my Yoga practise. 
It’s not just calming, but also gives me strength and resilience to get through everything during the week.

I’ve not done a yoga reel in a while. Was really working on opening up those tense muscles…
Tried the “compass pose” today (Parivrtta Surya Yantrasana) after warming up in #skandadana 
Ofcourse it needs to get better and it’s work in progress. But happy that I’ve got this far today! 

#yogapractice🧘‍♀️ #asanajunkie #yogababy #compasspose #skandasana #makeachdaycount

latestPosts.caption:
I love everything Italian….. The all new @celinimumbai at the @grandhyattmumbai felt like we were transported to beautiful Italy. 
The live culinary performance by Chef Alessio made it a food lovers delight and an unforgettable experience! 

With authentic Italian ingredients, the food was a great blend of modern global influences! 

The space and the setting had a quaint Italian charm, just perfect for cozy dinners with your date or a celebration with the family.

A fabulous experience indeed with my forever date @gaurrimalhotra 

#HometoItaly #Celini
#SurprisingYou #grandhyattmumbai

latestPosts.caption:
A late post, but this one deserves a special mention.
Had the honour and privilege of being invited as a jury member for #chrysalis2025 . If you are from the fashion industry, you know that the @sndtwuinsta , Fashion Design degree course, hold its coveted graduating show each year , which was being formally held after a 5 year gap,this year. Got to witness some incredible work from the finest talent and here’s wishing them the very best for their future in the business of fashion.

Thank you @jasminesarupria @jinalsangani and @sndtwuinsta for having me.

In some@great company with @narendra_kumar_bespoke @ferozadalal @meher2005 @jinalsangani 

And a glimpse of some of my favourite collections, that we evaluated during the jury.
#juryduty #latergram #sndtuniversity #fashiondesigndegreecourse #youngturks #freshbatch
